有些部分你必须选择要查看的 POV。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>将于 2023 年 11 月 9 日上映的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/like-a-dragon-gaiden-revives-kiryu-on-november-9th-2023-204950865.html"><em>《如龙外传：抹去他名字的男人》</em></a>也在此次活动中亮相。这是 Yakuza 系列的下一部作品，将再次由之前假死的桐生主演。 Epic Games 还发布了<em>Fortnite</em>最新一季的电影预告片，名为<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/fortnites-next-season-features-transformers-and-rideable-raptors-210411943.html"><em>Fortnite Wilds</em></a> ，将于 6 月 9 日上映。最后，Square Enix 推出了<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-vii-remake-rebirth-is-delayed-to-early-2024-211301245.html"><em>《最终幻想 VII 重制版：重生》</em></a>的首映预告片，这是<em>《最终幻想 7》</em>重制版的第二章，已推迟到 2024 年初。</p><p>您可以在上面的视频中观看不到 20 分钟的所有这些公告以及更多内容。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/watch-the-summer-game-fest-keynote-in-under-20-minutes-091517818.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/watch-the-summer-game-fest-keynote-in-under-20-minutes-091517818.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 04df29e9-06cc-460e-8df5-9ba608dc3742</guid><dc:creator>玛丽拉月亮</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 09 Jun 2023 09:15:17 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686312015</ingested><modified> 2023-06-09T12:00:19+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="1020" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/8def7eb0-0699-11ee-bfff-ac331615490c" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1020" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/8def7eb0-0699-11ee-bfff-ac331615490c" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Square Enix]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A screenshot of the upcoming Final Fantasy VII Remake: Rebirth showing the character Cloud in foreground.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Final Fantasy VII Remake: Rebirth]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Logitech retires the Blue microphone brand]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>罗技正在摆脱<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/blue-yeti-nano-microphone-irl-143058272.html">Blue 麦克风品牌</a>，现在将以 Logitech G 游戏品牌销售产品——只保留 Blue 名称以“描述我们的技术”，它说。 Blue 已从其网站上罗技的“品牌”部分中删除，而 Bluemic.com 域现在指向罗技。所有 Blue 产品，包括 Yeti、Snowball 等，现在<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5sb2dpdGVjaGcuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL3N0cmVhbWluZy1nZWFyLmh0bWwiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjY5OGRhYTk2LTE5Y2QtNDRmNi1iMTc3LTRkY2ZlZjM2ZTE0MyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAR0pskuuGBpo1Fj0JmYMQMGqpzcbr9xhW6vfDcZmEq7H&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fstreaming-gear.html" class="rapid-with-clickid">只能在其网站的罗技 G 部分找到</a>。</p><p>据<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/8/23589618/logitech-blue-now-yeti-astro-merge-logitech-g-brands"><em>The Verge</em></a>报道，该公司还将其 Astro 高端游戏耳机、混音器等转移到罗技 G，但将保留该品牌。 “Astro 品牌将继续作为 Logitech G 品牌下的高级控制台音频产品系列继续存在。请继续关注有关 ASTRO 的更多信息，包括我们认为我们的社区将非常兴奋的发布，”该公司在常见问题解答中表示在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/LogitechG/comments/144htiu/an_update_from_logitech_g/?sf178951114=1">Reddit</a>上。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="23485035d6964b0993e2dac1bcd852ba"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">👋 游戏玩家和创作者！我们有关于罗技 G、 <a href="https://twitter.com/ASTROGaming?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@ASTROGaming</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/BlueMicrophones?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@BlueMicrophones</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/logitechc?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@logitechc</a>之间即将进行的品牌合并的最新消息！ <a href="https://t.co/qPPT36sJr6">pic.twitter.com/qPPT36sJr6</a></p> - 罗技 G (@LogitechG) <a href="https://twitter.com/LogitechG/status/1666883158787104768?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 6 月 8 日</a></blockquote></div><p>罗技已经暗示它可能会取消 Blue 品牌，并于去年年底发布了罗技 G 旗下的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/logitech-litra-beam-key-light-blue-sona-microphone-160043897.html">Blue Sona 流媒体麦克风</a>。不久前，它还更改了对 Yeti 麦克风的描述，将其描述为采用 Blue VO!CE 技术的 Yeti 麦克风。</p><p>罗技于 2018 年以 1.17 亿美元<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-07-30-blue-logitech-acquisition.html">收购了 Blue</a> 。然而，Blue Microphones 的历史超出您的预期，在开发任何流媒体产品之前最初创造了“Bottle”麦克风（根据<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blue_Microphones">维基百科</a>，Blue 也代表“Baltic Latvian Universal Electronics”）。它的第一款专为流式音频设计的麦克风是 Snowball，在 Logitech 上仍以<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5sb2dpdGVjaGcuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL3N0cmVhbWluZy1nZWFyL3Nub3diYWxsLWljZS11c2ItbWljcm9waG9uZS45ODgtMDAwMDY3Lmh0bWwiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjY5OGRhYTk2LTE5Y2QtNDRmNi1iMTc3LTRkY2ZlZjM2ZTE0MyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQnkMrLiDPd5hNbo5Qlm9g0QU8q-BggmJtI3OocFRbZJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fstreaming-gear%2Fsnowball-ice-usb-microphone.988-000067.html" class="rapid-with-clickid">Snowball Ice 的形式出售，售价 50 美元</a>。</p><p>鉴于 Blue 品牌在播客、流媒体和其他领域备受推崇，为了支持其声望远低于其声望的品牌而将其关闭似乎是一个奇怪的选择。该公司承诺与其所有罗技 G 产品进行“更深入的集成”，并承诺您将能够“在一个地方”配置它们，大概是其 G HUB 应用程序。如果这是计划，那么 Logitech 可能需要解决对该应用程序的批评，如果<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/LogitechG/comments/144htiu/an_update_from_logitech_g/?sf178951114=1">其 Reddit 常见问题解答帖子上的评论</a>可以作为参考的话。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/logitech-retires-the-blue-microphone-brand-083111975.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/logitech-retires-the-blue-microphone-brand-083111975.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 698daa96-19cd-44f6-b177-4dcfef36e143</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 09 Jun 2023 08:31:11 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686299472</ingested><modified> 2023-06-09T08:31:19+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1440" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/137a5340-069d-11ee-ae59-b37f5febc9bb" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1440" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/202